  <entry>
    <title>ssh免密登录</title>
    <url>/2021/02/24/ssh%E5%85%8D%E5%AF%86%E7%99%BB%E5%BD%95/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<blockquote class="blockquote-center">
            <i class="fa fa-quote-left"></i>
            <p>生如蝼蚁，当立鸿鹄之志；</p>
<p>命薄似纸，应有不屈之心；</p>
<p>乾坤未定，你我都是黑马！</p>

            <i class="fa fa-quote-right"></i>
          </blockquote>

<span id="more"></span>

<h3 id="0x01-前言"><a href="#0x01-前言" class="headerlink" title="0x01  前言"></a>0x01  前言</h3><p>每次ssh登陆linux服务器都要手动输入账号密码,很麻烦。于是记录一下linux免密登录的方法。</p>
<h3 id="0x02-免密登录ssh"><a href="#0x02-免密登录ssh" class="headerlink" title="0x02  免密登录ssh"></a>0x02  免密登录ssh</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">在windows的用户目录下创建.ssh目录:mkdir ~&#x2F;.ssh</span><br><span class="line">cd .ssh</span><br><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C &quot;1292678975@qq.com&quot;,后面接3个回车</span><br><span class="line">登录linux服务器</span><br><span class="line">mkdir ~&#x2F;.ssh</span><br><span class="line">vi ~&#x2F;.ssh&#x2F;authorized_keys</span><br><span class="line">把刚才.ssh目录下生成的id_rsa.pub文件发送到linux根目录</span><br><span class="line">cat ~&#x2F;id_rsa.pub &gt;&gt; ~&#x2F;.ssh&#x2F;authorized_keys</span><br><span class="line">删除服务器的id_rsa.pub:rm ~&#x2F;id_rsa.pub</span><br><span class="line">重启ssh服务:service sshd restart</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="0x03-配置ssh会话永不过期"><a href="#0x03-配置ssh会话永不过期" class="headerlink" title="0x03  配置ssh会话永不过期"></a>0x03  配置ssh会话永不过期</h3><figure class="highlight txt"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vi /etc/ssh/sshd_config</span><br><span class="line">ClientAliveInterval 60</span><br><span class="line">ClientAliveCountMax 3</span><br><span class="line">service sshd restart</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



]]></content>
